/**
 * @a0n/distributed-inference-host
 *
 * Workspace-shared shim wrapping the wasm32 build of
 * open-source/gnosis/distributed-inference. Provides:
 *   - knot file header parsing
 *   - R2 / HTTP / FS Range fetching via a single KnotByteSource interface
 *   - layer prefetch with LRU eviction
 *   - the orchestration sequence between async fetches and sync WASM calls
 *
 * Every Worker that runs distributed inference imports this package so the
 * orchestration logic stays in one place.
 */

